A '''television''' was a piece of technology. The swiveling of the sensory apparatus on the head of [[Greedo/Legends|Greedo]] the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] was reminiscent of satellite antennas scanning for television channels.<ref name="Be Still My Heart">"[[Be Still My Heart: The Bartender's Tale]]" &ndash; ''[[Tales from the Mos Eisley Cantina]]''</ref>

{{Noncanonstart|legends=1}}
[[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku]] used one of these large televisions to view the battle over [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. However, the set would not operate correctly, so he called in [[General/Legends|General]] [[Grievous/Legends|Grievous]] to act as an antenna, which improved the picture.<ref name="LEGO Star Wars: Revenge of the Brick">''[[LEGO Star Wars: Revenge of the Brick]]''</ref>
{{Noncanonend}}

